{{For|the [[Consul]] in {{XC3FR|sublink}}|Q (FR)}}{{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = Q |image = Consul Q.png |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Male |haircolor = |eyecolor = |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = |voiceactoreng = }} '''Q''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == Q is the [[Consul]] of [[Colony 30]].
== Story == Q first appears when his colony's commander, [[Valdi]], fails to report to him and work on the [[Ferronis]]. He introduces himself to the party but is not interested in fighting them at the time. Q instead coerces Valdi to continue working on the [[Levnis]]es. Q is initially satisfied with Valdi's cooperation, but upon realizing the mechanic meant to sabotage the project, he attacks him. Q begins piloting the [[Incomplete Siege-Lev]], and fights the party. He seemingly dies after the Levnis gets destroyed.
He is revealed to have survived during ''[[Inescapable Past]]'' and attempts to sabotage an alliance between Colony 30 and [[Colony Iota]], and having learned of her past from [[E]] he seeks to kill her as she killed her previous commander. The party confronts him and defeats him, this time for good. {{clr}}
== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Moebius Q |image = Moebius Q.png |caption = Moebius Q |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Moebius]] |level = 59 |area = [[Rae-Bel Tableland]] ([[Old Kana Battlefield]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Inescapable Past]]'' |respawn = No |movement = Ground |detection = |exp = 4,032 |cp = 400 |sp = 0 |gold = 0 |hp = 2,530,800 |strength = 1,135 |healing = 374 |dexterity = 244 |agility = 193 |physdef = 0% |ethdef = 0% |critrate = 0% |guardrate = 0% }} '''Moebius Q''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]]. He is a Moebius fought at level 59 at [[Old Kana Battlefield]] in [[Rae-Bel Tableland]] during ''[[Inescapable Past]]''.
