== Quotes == === Boss === *''"Cease your useless resistance."'' *''"You cannot hope to defeat me."'' *''"Just desserts for those who oppose the world."'' *''"Ether supply: powering laser."'' *''"Eyesore!"'' *''"Make your peace."'' *''"Rise if you like, it matters not."'' *''"Ouroboros! You have no right to exist."'' *''"You will be cleansed."'' *''"Firing missiles!"'' *''"Purge the rebels!"'' *''"How brittle, these impudent beings."''
== Trivia == * The false Queen's voice effect changes for each of the three times she speaks in-game. When first appearing in Chapter 2, she has a slight filter effect due to her mask similar to her Kevesi counterpart; when giving her speech in Chapter 5, she has no voice effects and sounds identical to her template; and during her boss battle with her Ferronis activated, her voice has a heavy metallic echo and reverb. * The false Queen uses the same model as Nia in all instances outside of battle. As such, hacking to remove her mask only reveals Nia's face. * There is no way for the player to get a Hero to fight alongside them for the Boss Battle against the false Queen.
