{{For|the [[Consul]] in {{XC3FR|sublink}}|R (FR)}} {{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = R |image = Consul_R.jpg |species = [[Moebius]] |age = |gender = Female |haircolor = |eyecolor = |affiliation = [[Consul]]s |appearances = {{XC3}} |voiceactorjp = [[wikipedia:Sayaka Kinoshita|Sayaka Kinoshita]] |voiceactoreng = [https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0499014/ Laurel Lefkow] }} '''R''' is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == R is the [[Consul]] of [[Colony 11]]. She first makes an appearance commenting on [[Joran|J]]. She is later defeated by [[Ashera]] and [[Ouroboros]] in Colony 11, but is spared, and makes her escape, vowing to take revenge.
Later, she launches an assault on the colony with zombified puppet soldiers from both Keves and Agnus, with the help of Consul [[W]]'s powers. After pushing Ashera, Ouroboros, and her commanders back to the colony gates, she challenges Ashera to a duel at [[Hovering Reef 0]], before calling off her attack. {{clr}}
== Story == At some point, despite being in charge of Colony 11, R is in control of an [[Agnus|Agnian]] [[Colony|colony]] where they fought against Consul [[V]]'s Kelvesi Colony, only to lose to them causing the Consul to berate her Agnian soldiers to be useless pawns.
